dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Map titles: Calcutta and environs -- Shanghai and environs -- Vicinity of Hong Kong and Canton -- Vicinity of Peking and Taku -- Island of Singapore -- Island and town of Bombay -- Madras and environs -- Bombay and environs -- Calcutta -- Saigon and environs -- The island of Ceylon. Running title in margin: Library atlas of the world. [Asia detail maps]. 90. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
